 Following up on the hugely successful first edition, at the peak of a sizzling summer, we offer you the second selection of our Uplifting Trance block busters: Best Of Uplifting Trance 2014 Volume 2.
 The first Edition successfully charted in the British Dance Albums Top 40 earlier this year and similarly in many other territories and we expect Volume 2 to have the same impact! Included are hits from Tenishia & Ana Criado, Nitrous Oxide & Neev Kennedy, Allan & Envy and Elles de Graaf, Space RockerZ & Cathy Burton, Denise Rivera, Beat Service, Feel feat. Jan Johnston, Susana & Hazem Beltagui and many many more Trancefloor Uplifting killers. Enjoy!
